ova, Marieke van der Werf, Emma Wiltshire, Andrea W\u00fcrz--> |url=https://www.ecdc.europa.eu/sites/default/files/documents/covid-19-social-distancing-measuresg-guide-second-update.pdf |title=Considerations relating to social distancing measures in response to COVID-19 \u2013 second update |date=23 March 2020 |publisher=European Centre for Disease Prevention and Control |access-date=24 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"PWea7\">{{cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/if-you-are-sick/steps-when-sick.html |title=What To Do if You Are Sick with COVID-19 |date=11 February 2020 |website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention|url-status=live|access-date=17 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"0DNOZ\">{{cite web |url=https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/covid-19-stay-at-home-guidance/stay-at-home-guidance-for-households-with-possible-coronavirus-covid-19-infection |title=Stay at home: guidance for households with possible coronavirus (COVID-19) infection |publisher=Government of the United Kingdom |access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"W4DaA\">{{Cite news |last=Horowitz |first=Jason |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/09/world/europe/italy-lockdown-coronavirus.html |title=Italy Announces Restrictions Over Entire Country in Attempt to Halt Coronavirus |date=9 March 2020 |work=The New York Times|access-date=20 March 2020 |issn=0362-4331}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Q8Eyd\">{{cite news |url=https://www.cnn.com/2020/03/20/politics/new-york-workforce-stay-home/index.html |title=Cuomo orders all nonessential New York workers to stay home |first=Veronica |last=Stracqualursi |publisher=CNN|access-date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"VQaNX\">{{cite web |url=https://www.cdc.gov/coronavirus/2019-ncov/travelers/after-travel-precautions.html |title=COVID-19 Travel Precautions |date=11 February 2020 |work=US [[Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] |url-status=live |access-date=6 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RnW59\">{{cite journal |last1=Qualls |first1=Noreen |last2=Levitt |first2=Alexandra |last3=Kanade |first3=Neha |last4=Wright-Jegede |first4=Narue |last5=Dopson |first5=Stephanie |last6=Biggerstaff |first6=Matthew |last7=Reed |first7=Carrie |last8=Uzicanin |first8=Amra |last9=Levitt |first9=Alexandra |last10=Dopson |first10=Stephanie |last11=Frank |first11=Mark |last12=Holloway |first12=Rachel |last13=Koonin |first13=Lisa |last14=Rasmussen |first14=Sonja |last15=Redd |first15=Stephen |last16=de la Motte Hurst |first16=Christopher |last17=Kanade |first17=Neha |last18=Qualls |first18=Noreen |last19=Rainey |first19=Jeanette |last20=Uzicanin |first20=Amra |last21=Biggerstaff |first21=Matthew |last22=Jernigan |first22=Daniel |last23=Reed |first23=Carrie |title=Community Mitigation Guidelines to Prevent Pandemic Influenza\u2014United States, 2017 |journal=MMWR. Recommendations and Reports |date=21 April 2017 |volume=66 |issue=1 |pages=1\u201334 |doi=10.15585/mmwr.rr6601a1 |pmid=28426646 |pmc=5837128}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"NY0JD\">{{cite web |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/news-desk/what-it-means-to-contain-and-mitigate-the-coronavirus |title=What It Means to Contain and Mitigate the Coronavirus |first=Robert P. |last=Baird |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The New Yorker]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"RwmYm\">{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2020/03/07/world/asia/china-coronavirus-cost.html |title=China May Be Beating the Coronavirus, at a Painful Cost |first=Amy |last=Qin |work=[[The New York Times]] |date=7 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"shZdf\">{{cite web |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2020/mar/11/mass-testing-alerts-and-big-fines-the-strategies-used-in-asia-to-slow-coronavirus |title=Mass testing, alerts and big fines: the strategies used in Asia to slow coronavirus |first1=Justin McCurry Rebecca Ratcliffe in |last1=Bangkok |first2=Helen Davidson in Hong |last2=Kong |date=11 March 2020 |work=[[The Guardian]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"hxm4a\">{{cite web |url=https://www.ebmedicine.net/topics/i